/*]]>*/</style></p>
<div class=3D"toc-macro rbtoc1485852259482">=20
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">=20
<li><a href=3D"#Configurethenavigation-PlatformUINavigationHub">PlatformUI =
Navigation Hub</a></li>=20
<li><a href=3D"#Configurethenavigation-Addinganewnavigationitem">Adding a n=
ew navigation item</a>=20
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">=20
<li><a href=3D"#Configurethenavigation-PluginfortheNavigationHubviewservice=
">Plugin for the Navigation Hub view service</a></li>=20
