s/ExtendingPlatformUIConferenceBundle/releases/tag/5_navigation" class=3D"e=
xternal-link" rel=3D"nofollow">the 5_navigation tag on GitHub</a>, this ste=
p result can also be viewed as <a href=3D"https://github.com/ezsystems/Exte=
ndingPlatformUIConferenceBundle/compare/4_view...5_navigation" class=3D"ext=
ernal-link" rel=3D"nofollow">a diff between tags <code>4_view</code> and <c=
ode>5_navigation</code></a>.</p>
<p>The next step is then <a href=3D"/display/TECHDOC/Build+the+content+list=
">to build and display the content list</a>.</p>
